a close, we=E2=80=99re
grateful for another year filled with remarkable work from our journalists =
at Puck HQ in New York and across our bureaus in Hollywood, Washington, and=
 more.

In this second installment of our annual Guide to Mirth & Merriment, the Pu=
ck family and a handful of V.I.P. friends are excited to share a few wardro=
be essentials that we=E2=80=99re angling to add to our closets this year=E2=
=80=94from timeless staples to standout statement pieces. (P.S.: If you buy=
 anything, we may earn a commission!) Thanks to all
of our contributors, and also our friends at Netflix, for their support.

